title: Manchester United’s Europa League rivals Anderlecht admit they are SCARED of beating Jose Mourinho’s side
text:
Devil may care Manchester United’s Europa League rivals Anderlecht admit they are SCARED of beating Jose Mourinho’s side 
Club chief executive Herman van Holsbeeck said victory would lead to a fixture pile-up that threatened to wreck their hopes of a domestic title By Steve Goodman
